text: Golfech is a former railway station in Golfech, Occitanie, France. ==The station== The station is on the Bordeaux–Sète railway. The station was served by TER (local) services operated by SNCF, between Agen and Toulouse. ==References== *Timetables TER Midi-Pyrénées Category:Railway stations in Tarn-et-Garonne Category:Defunct railway stations in Occitanie
title: Golfech station
